{"tid":1313637,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【PS官方推特分享PS4豆知識 炸出一片玩家「這麼多年PS4白玩了！」】","createTime":"2019-07-13T23:53:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T11:51:09.000Z","uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c4076ba1814e3441a96b87f493a817bc77e94ab","tid":1313637,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T23:53:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/posts/1286330474868161\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNmia.Gaming%2Fposts%2F1286330474868161&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtUL5WZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=d339a5cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Nmia.Gaming/posts/1286330474868161</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NthviED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNthviED.jpg&h=89382718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【PS官方推特分享PS4豆知識 炸出一片玩家「這麼多年PS4白玩了！」】</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n不久前PS英國官方推特給大家介紹了一個豆知識「在隱藏獎杯的詳細頁按方塊鍵就可以顯示其內容」，結果意外的是居然有很多人不知道<br />\n<br />\n由此其他推主們紛紛分享一些其它的操作比如「長按PS鍵10秒可以關閉手柄電源」、「連按兩下PS鍵可以快速回到遊戲」、「在獎杯總覽頁按OPTION可以從互聯網搜索解法」、「手柄光條可以調亮度」等等，讓不少人驚呼這麼多年PS4白玩了。<br />\n<br />\n其實這些在用戶手冊（以及版本更新信息）裡都有&hellip;&hellip;就是好多人可能都沒有仔細讀過WWW<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bWBgec4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbWBgec4.jpg&h=bae44b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>按方塊鍵就可以顯示隱藏獎杯內容</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vQkXH6q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvQkXH6q.jpg&h=b80e39ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>在獎杯總覽頁按OPTION可以從互聯網搜索解法</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OLQgYEL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOLQgYEL.jpg&h=14a3763f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>手柄光條可以調亮度</em>"},{"pid":"eaddb557c3fc418238fde330c00165ef684b1639","tid":1313637,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T23:55